citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:25 AM on
29-Nov-18.
Inspector arrival to facility at 11:25 AM. Knocked on house front door. Called primary contact # (xxx-4628) and left
message. Went to kennel building and knocked on door. Honked car horn several times. No personnel visible on
premise or kennel. Inspector departure at 12:00 PM.
